*.gz

# Per-output preprocessing provenance sidecars (#158) are NOT committed: they
# carry a `generated:` timestamp that churns on every re-run, so committed
# copies showed up as spurious diffs / dirty working trees. They're regenerated
# by preprocess.py (and `sspsygene preprocess` / deploy --preprocess); load-db
# reads them at build time when present and stores NULL when absent.
*.preprocessing.yaml
